flags.alt: The flag of Zimbabwe is composed of seven equal horizontal bands of green, yellow, red, black, red, yellow and green, with a white isosceles triangle superimposed on the hoist side of the field. A yellow Zimbabwe bird superimposed on a five-pointed red star is centered in the triangle.
